  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the average risk for thyroid irradiation for any
      type of paediatric cardiac catheterization, based on the cummulative at-risk dose of 100 mSv,
      adjusted to the measured thyroid volume and to the patient's age.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
